---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy - SkillStart Jobs" description="How and why cookies are used.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumbs"><a href="/">Home</a> / Cookie Policy</div>
      <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="content-card">
        <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> April 19, 2026</p>
        <p>This Cookie Policy explains how SkillStart Jobs (&ldquo;we,&rdquo; &ldquo;us,&rdquo; or &ldquo;our&rdquo;) uses cookies and similar technologies when you visit skillstartjobs.online.</p>
        <p>By continuing to use our website, you agree to the use of cookies as described in this policy, subject to applicable laws and consent requirements.</p>

        <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
        <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device (computer, mobile phone, or tablet) when you visit a website.</p>
        <p>They help websites function properly, remember preferences, improve performance, and measure usage.</p>
        <p>Cookies may be:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Session Cookies - deleted when you close your browser</li>
          <li>Persistent Cookies - remain for a set period or until deleted</li>
          <li>First-Party Cookies - set by our website</li>
          <li>Third-Party Cookies - set by external services</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How SkillStart Jobs Uses Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use cookies and similar technologies to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Improve website functionality</li>
          <li>Remember user preferences</li>
          <li>Analyze traffic and usage behavior</li>
          <li>Measure performance</li>
          <li>Enhance user experience</li>
          <li>Support advertising and monetization</li>
          <li>Detect abuse or suspicious activity</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
        <p><strong>A. Essential Cookies</strong></p>
        <p>These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly.</p>
        <p>They may help with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Security</li>
          <li>Navigation</li>
          <li>Page loading</li>
          <li>Basic site operations</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Without these cookies, some parts of the website may not work correctly.</p>

        <p><strong>B. Performance & Analytics Cookies</strong></p>
        <p>These cookies help us understand how visitors use the website.</p>
        <p>They may collect data such as:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Pages visited</li>
          <li>Time spent on pages</li>
          <li>Device/browser type</li>
          <li>Traffic source</li>
          <li>General location data</li>
          <li>Click behavior</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This helps us improve website quality and content.</p>
        <p>We may use services such as Google Analytics.</p>

        <p><strong>C. Advertising Cookies</strong></p>
        <p>We may display ads through third-party partners such as Google AdSense.</p>
        <p>Advertising cookies may be used to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Show personalized or non-personalized ads</li>
          <li>Limit repeated ads</li>
          <li>Measure ad performance</li>
          <li>Improve ad relevance</li>
          <li>Prevent fraud</li>
        </ul>
        <p>These cookies may consider your previous browsing activity across websites, subject to applicable law.</p>

        <p><strong>D. Preference Cookies</strong></p>
        <p>These cookies may remember settings such as:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Language preference</li>
          <li>Consent choices</li>
          <li>Device-related settings</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Google AdSense Cookies</h2>
        <p>Third-party vendors, including Google, may use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this and other websites.</p>
        <p>Google may use advertising cookies to enable it and its partners to serve ads based on your browsing behavior.</p>
        <p>You can learn more here:</p>
        <p><a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads</a></p>
        <p>You can manage ad personalization here:</p>
        <p><a href="https://adssettings.google.com/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">https://adssettings.google.com/</a></p>

        <h2>5. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
        <p>Some cookies on our site may be set by third-party services we use, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Analytics providers</li>
          <li>Advertising networks</li>
          <li>Embedded content providers</li>
          <li>Security tools</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not directly control third-party cookies once set through their services.</p>
        <p>Please review their privacy or cookie policies for more information.</p>

        <h2>6. Your Cookie Choices</h2>
        <p>You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings.</p>
        <p>Most browsers allow you to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Delete cookies</li>
          <li>Block all cookies</li>
          <li>Block third-party cookies</li>
          <li>Clear browsing data</li>
          <li>Receive alerts before cookies are stored</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Please note that disabling cookies may affect functionality of some site features.</p>

        <h2>7. Consent Banner</h2>
        <p>Where required by law, SkillStart Jobs may display a cookie consent banner allowing users to accept, reject, or customize cookie preferences.</p>
        <p>Your choices may be stored for future visits.</p>

        <h2>8. Do Not Track Signals</h2>
        <p>Some browsers offer &ldquo;Do Not Track&rdquo; signals. Because no universal standard currently exists, our website may not respond consistently to such signals.</p>

        <h2>9. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Cookies may remain on your device for different periods depending on their purpose:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Session cookies expire after browser close</li>
          <li>Persistent cookies remain until expiration or deletion</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>10. Updates to This Cookie Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time due to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Legal requirements</li>
          <li>Technology changes</li>
          <li>Advertising updates</li>
          <li>Website improvements</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Updated versions will be posted on this page with a revised date.</p>

        <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions regarding this Cookie Policy, please contact us through the <a href="/contact/">Contact Page</a> on skillstartjobs.online.</p>

        <h2>12. Summary</h2>
        <p>By using SkillStart Jobs, you understand that cookies may be used to improve functionality, analytics, and advertising experiences while helping keep the platform free for users.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
